#. <section class="sutta" id="sn41.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn41.10:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 41"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 41"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn41.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Cittavagga"
msgstr "1. With Citta"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn41.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Gilānadassanasutta"
msgstr "10. Seeing the Sick"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn41.10:1.1"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena citto gahapati ābādhiko hoti dukkhito bāḷhagilāno."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time the householder Citta was sick, suffering, gravely ill."

msgctxt "sn41.10:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho sambahulā ārāmadevatā vanadevatā rukkhadevatā osadhitiṇavanappatīsu "
"adhivatthā devatā saṅgamma samāgamma cittaṃ gahapatiṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr ""
"Then several deities of the parks, forests, trees, and those who haunt the "
"herbs, grass, and big trees came together and said to Citta:"

msgctxt "sn41.10:1.3"
msgid "“paṇidhehi, gahapati, anāgatamaddhānaṃ rājā assaṃ cakkavattī”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Householder, make a wish to become a wheel-turning monarch in the future!”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.303"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn41.10:2.1"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ vutte, citto gahapati tā ārāmadevatā vanadevatā rukkhadevatā "
"osadhitiṇavanappatīsu adhivatthā devatā etadavoca:"
msgstr "When they said this, Citta said to them:"

msgctxt "sn41.10:2.2"
msgid "“tampi aniccaṃ, tampi addhuvaṃ, tampi pahāya gamanīyan”ti."
msgstr ""
"“That too is impermanent! That too will pass! That too will be left behind!”"

msgctxt "sn41.10:2.3"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ vutte, cittassa gahapatino mittāmaccā ñātisālohitā cittaṃ gahapatiṃ "
"etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr ""
"When he said this, his friends and colleagues, relatives and family members "
"said:"

msgctxt "sn41.10:2.4"
msgid "“satiṃ, ayyaputta, upaṭṭhapehi, mā vippalapī”ti."
msgstr "“Be mindful, lord! Don’t babble.”"

msgctxt "sn41.10:2.5"
msgid "“Kiṃ tāhaṃ vadāmi yaṃ maṃ tumhe evaṃ vadetha:"
msgstr "“What have I said that makes you say that?”"

msgctxt "sn41.10:2.6"
msgid "‘satiṃ, ayyaputta, upaṭṭhapehi, mā vippalapī’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn41.10:2.7"
msgid "“Evaṃ kho tvaṃ, ayyaputta, vadesi:"
msgstr "“It’s because you said:"

msgctxt "sn41.10:2.8"
msgid "‘tampi aniccaṃ, tampi addhuvaṃ, tampi pahāya gamanīyan’”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘That too is impermanent! That too will pass! That too will be left behind!’”"

msgctxt "sn41.10:2.9"
msgid ""
"“Tathā hi pana maṃ ārāmadevatā vanadevatā rukkhadevatā osadhitiṇavanappatīsu "
"adhivatthā devatā evamāhaṃsu:"
msgstr ""
"“Oh, well, that’s because the deities of the parks, forests, trees, and "
"those who haunt the herbs, grass, and big trees said to me:"

msgctxt "sn41.10:2.10"
msgid "‘paṇidhehi, gahapati, anāgatamaddhānaṃ rājā assaṃ cakkavattī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Householder, make a wish to become a wheel-turning monarch in the future!’"

msgctxt "sn41.10:2.11"
msgid "Tāhaṃ evaṃ vadāmi:"
msgstr "So I said to them:"

msgctxt "sn41.10:2.12"
msgid "‘tampi aniccaṃ … pe … tampi pahāya gamanīyan’”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘That too is impermanent! That too will pass! That too will be left behind!’”"

msgctxt "sn41.10:2.13"
msgid ""
"“Kiṃ pana tā, ayyaputta, ārāmadevatā vanadevatā rukkhadevatā "
"osadhitiṇavanappatīsu adhivatthā devatā atthavasaṃ sampassamānā evamāhaṃsu:"
msgstr "“But what reason do they see for saying that to you?”"

msgctxt "sn41.10:2.14"
msgid "‘paṇidhehi, gahapati, anāgatamaddhānaṃ rājā assaṃ cakkavattī’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn41.10:2.15"
msgid ""
"“Tāsaṃ kho ārāmadevatānaṃ vanadevatānaṃ rukkhadevatānaṃ "
"osadhitiṇavanappatīsu adhivatthānaṃ devatānaṃ evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "“They think:"

#. VAR: sīlavā → sīlavanto (mr)
msgctxt "sn41.10:2.16"
msgid "‘ayaṃ kho citto gahapati, sīlavā kalyāṇadhammo."
msgstr "‘This householder Citta is ethical, of good character."

msgctxt "sn41.10:2.17"
msgid "Sace paṇidahissati—"
msgstr "If he makes a wish to"

# Following readings as per BB. Punctuation in MS is incorrect.
msgctxt "sn41.10:2.18"
msgid ""
"anāgatamaddhānaṃ rājā assaṃ cakkavattī’ti, ‘tassa kho ayaṃ ijjhissati, "
"sīlavato cetopaṇidhi visuddhattā dhammiko dhammikaṃ phalaṃ anupassatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"become a wheel-turning monarch in the future, his heart’s wish will succeed "
"because of the purity of his ethics. And then as a proper, principled king "
"he will provide proper spirit-offerings.’"

msgctxt "sn41.10:2.19"
msgid ""
"Imaṃ kho tā ārāmadevatā vanadevatā rukkhadevatā osadhitiṇavanappatīsu "
"adhivatthā devatā atthavasaṃ sampassamānā evamāhaṃsu:"
msgstr "That’s the reason they see for saying to me:"

msgctxt "sn41.10:2.20"
msgid "‘paṇidhehi, gahapati, anāgatamaddhānaṃ rājā assaṃ cakkavattī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Householder, make a wish to become a wheel-turning monarch in the future!’"

msgctxt "sn41.10:2.21"
msgid "Tāhaṃ evaṃ vadāmi:"
msgstr "So I said to them:"

msgctxt "sn41.10:2.22"
msgid "‘tampi aniccaṃ, tampi addhuvaṃ, tampi pahāya gamanīyan’”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘That too is impermanent! That too will pass! That too will be left behind!’”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.304"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn41.10:3.1"
msgid "“Tena hi, ayyaputta, amhepi ovadāhī”ti."
msgstr "“Then, lord, advise us!”"

msgctxt "sn41.10:3.2"
msgid "“Tasmā hi vo evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ—"
msgstr "“So you should train like this:"

msgctxt "sn41.10:3.3"
msgid "buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgatā bhavissāma:"
msgstr "We will have experiential confidence in the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn41.10:3.4"
msgid ""
"‘itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū "
"anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘That Blessed One is perfected, a fully awakened Buddha, accomplished in "
"knowledge and conduct, holy, knower of the world, supreme guide for those "
"who wish to train, teacher of gods and humans, awakened, blessed.’"

msgctxt "sn41.10:3.5"
msgid "Dhamme aveccappasādena samannāgatā bhavissāma:"
msgstr "We will have experiential confidence in the teaching:"

msgctxt "sn41.10:3.6"
msgid ""
"‘svākkhāto bhagavatā dhammo sandiṭṭhiko akāliko ehipassiko opaneyyiko "
"paccattaṃ veditabbo viññūhī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘The teaching is well explained by the Buddha—realizable in this very life, "
"immediately effective, inviting inspection, relevant, so that sensible "
"people can know it for themselves.’"

msgctxt "sn41.10:3.7"
msgid "Saṅghe aveccappasādena samannāgatā bhavissāma:"
msgstr "We will have experiential confidence in the Saṅgha:"

msgctxt "sn41.10:3.8"
msgid ""
"‘suppaṭipanno bhagavato sāvakasaṅgho, ujuppaṭipanno bhagavato sāvakasaṅgho, "
"ñāyappaṭipanno bhagavato sāvakasaṅgho, sāmīcippaṭipanno bhagavato "
"sāvakasaṅgho, yadidaṃ cattāri purisayugāni aṭṭha purisapuggalā esa bhagavato "
"sāvakasaṅgho āhuneyyo pāhuneyyo dakkhiṇeyyo añjalikaraṇīyo anuttaraṃ "
"puññakkhettaṃ lokassā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘The Saṅgha of the Buddha’s disciples is practicing the way that’s good, "
"straightforward, methodical, and proper. It consists of the four pairs, the "
"eight individuals. This is the Saṅgha of the Buddha’s disciples that is "
"worthy of offerings dedicated to the gods, worthy of hospitality, worthy of "
"a teacher’s offering, worthy of greeting with joined palms, and is the "
"supreme field of merit for the world.’"

msgctxt "sn41.10:3.9"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ kho pana kiñci kule deyyadhammaṃ sabbaṃ taṃ appaṭivibhattaṃ bhavissati "
"sīlavantehi kalyāṇadhammehīti evañhi vo sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr ""
"And we will share without reservation all the gifts available to give in our "
"family with those who are ethical and of good character.”"

# I don’t see why Ee’s reading should be adopted as per BB. pasadetva is not used in this sense, so far as I know, in the prose suttas.
msgctxt "sn41.10:3.10"
msgid ""
"Atha kho citto gahapati mittāmacce ñātisālohite buddhe ca dhamme ca saṅghe "
"ca cāge ca samādapetvā kālamakāsīti."
msgstr ""
"Then, after Citta had encouraged his friends and colleagues, relatives and "
"family members in the Buddha, the teaching, the Saṅgha, and generosity, he "
"passed away."

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn41.10:3.11"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn41.10:3.12"
msgid "Cittavaggo paṭhamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn41.10:4.1"
msgid "Saṃyojanaṃ dve isidattā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn41.10:4.2"
msgid "Mahako kāmabhūpi ca;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn41.10:4.3"
msgid "Godatto ca nigaṇṭho ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn41.10:4.4"
msgid "Acelena gilānadassananti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "sn41.10:4.5"
msgid "Cittasaṃyuttaṃ samattaṃ."
msgstr "The Linked Discourses on Citta the Householder are complete."
